CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 19, 1956, pg. B13 reads: "Charmers - Debs, seated: The Misses Joycelyn Fountaine, Mae Louise Allen. Standing: The Misses Edna Price, Elaine Pooples [sic], Patti Ann Griffin and Elizabeth Wheeler."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, seated: Joycelyn Fountaine and Mae Louise Allen; standing: Edna Price, Elaine Pooples, Patti Ann Griffin, and Elizabeth Wheeler, posed in interior for Alpha Kappa Alpha's Fifth Debutante Cotillion, Syria Mosque
